      <title>集团首席财务官表示，阿达尼绿色美元债券可能在 2025 年中期恢复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/adani-green-dollar-bond-may-be-revived-mid-2025-group-cfo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[集团首席财务官 Jugeshinder Singh 周五表示，阿达尼绿色能源有限公司 (Adani Green Energy Ltd.) 将考虑在 4 月至 6 月期间重新发行已废除的美元债券，此举彰显了尽管美国对创始人 Gautam Adani 展开调查，该集团仍具有强大的韧性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/adani-green-dollar-bond-may-be-revived-mid-2025-group-cfo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 14:25:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Milei 首次阿根廷私有化遭遇 5.36 亿美元债务困扰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/milei-s-first-privatization-in-argentina-beset-by-536-million-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱 (Javier Milei) 设定 12 月为阿根廷首次将大量国有企业出售给私营部门的最后期限，这表明政府出售企业将面临巨大挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/milei-s-first-privatization-in-argentina-beset-by-536-million-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 14:15:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>维勒鲁瓦呼吁欧洲央行降息，因为通胀目标即将实现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/villeroy-calls-for-ecb-rate-cuts-as-inflation-target-in-sight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会成员弗朗索瓦·维勒鲁瓦·德加洛表示，欧洲央行应继续降息，因为欧元区通胀率可能在 2025 年上半年达到 2%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/villeroy-calls-for-ecb-rate-cuts-as-inflation-target-in-sight</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 13:58:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>道达尔能源计划投资 7.5 亿美元在尼日利亚建设天然气项目，以增加液化天然气供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/totalenergies-eyes-750-million-gas-project-in-nigeria-to-boost-lng-supplies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国能源巨头道达尔能源公司可能于明年批准在尼日利亚投资 7.5 亿美元的天然气项目，这可能表明这个非洲国家重振碳氢化合物生产投资的努力正在取得进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/totalenergies-eyes-750-million-gas-project-in-nigeria-to-boost-lng-supplies</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 13:57:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>公司债券 ETF 推动大宗交易激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/corporate-bond-etfs-are-fueling-a-rise-in-monster-block-trades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资组合交易的蓬勃发展，让投资者只需点击几下鼠标就能买入或卖出数十只公司债券，推动了几年前信贷市场上还罕见的大型交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/corporate-bond-etfs-are-fueling-a-rise-in-monster-block-trades</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 13:30:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度经济增长遭遇冲击 央行面临降息压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/india-s-economic-growth-weakens-to-almost-two-year-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度经济增速降至近两年来最低，这抑制了全年经济前景，也考验了总理纳伦德拉·莫迪雄心勃勃的增长计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/india-s-economic-growth-weakens-to-almost-two-year-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 10:41:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧元区通胀加速但不会阻止欧洲央行降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/euro-zone-inflation-accelerates-but-won-t-derail-ecb-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管欧元区通胀率已超过欧洲央行 2% 的目标，但官员们不太可能在下个月及以后继续降低利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/euro-zone-inflation-accelerates-but-won-t-derail-ecb-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
